I am *Italian*, and I know how traditionalists we are. Wherever we go, we look for Italian food, Italian clothes, Italian cars, and... *someone speaking Italian*. We share this feature with all the other Mediterranean peoples. Our Country is well known for the food, its nice weather, its culture, history, and music. But many ignore the fact that Italy has historically been harsh towards its sons and daughters, repeatedly forcing them to migrate in search for a better life.
